pan class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juni 29, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgz1719676396285.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgz1719676396285.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgz1719676396285.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rtb1665702783254\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $power\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"rtb1665702783254___power_280470\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Calculate the value of X raised to the power of Y (XY).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__topic_d87662e1_d87663e1_d87664e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87665e1_d87666e1_d87667e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$power</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Y</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__topic_d58382e1_d58383e1_d58384e1_d58385e1_d58386e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024183e82\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87671e1_d87672e1_d87673e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">Y</var>—numeric constant, or field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a numeric value.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__topic_d58387e1_d58388e1_d58389e1_d58390e1_d58391e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024183e97\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87677e1_d87678e1_d87679e1\">Calculated value of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> raised to the power of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Y</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87680e1_d87681e1_d87682e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$power</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Value \n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1204\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_NEGATIVE&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Negative value not allowed\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1207\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_UNDERFLOW&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Underflow\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1208\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_OVERFLOW&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Overflow\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n -1209\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n &lt;UPROCERR_DIVIDE&gt;\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rtb1665702783254__table_d9374e1_d9375e1_d9376e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n Divide by zero\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__topic_d58392e1_d58393e1_d58394e1_d58395e1_d58396e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024183e205\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__topic_d58397e1_d58398e1_d58399e1_d58400e1_d58401e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024183e215\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87692e1_d87693e1_d87694e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$power</span> calculates the value of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> raised to the power of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Y</var> ((XY).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87695e1_d87696e1_d87697e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> is less than zero, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Y</var> must be an integer.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__p_d87698e1_d87699e1_d87700e1\">The absolute value of the result of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$power</span> must be in the range 10 -9999 through 10 9999 , inclusive.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__section_qfq_rlz_wbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1024183e248\">Example: Calculating a Cube Root</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example computes the cube root of the value in MYFIELD:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rtb1665702783254__pre_tgf_slz_wbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vCubeRoot = $power(MYFIELD, 1/3)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424667\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7424667\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$power Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juni 29, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $power Calculate the value of X raised to the power of Y (XY). $power ( X , Y ) Parameters X and Y —numeric constant, or field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a numeric value. Return Values Calculated value of X raised to the power of Y . If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 1. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $power Value Error constant Meaning -1204 <UPROCERR_NEGATIVE> Negative value not allowed -1207 <UPROCERR_UNDERFLOW> Underflow -1208 <UPROCERR_OVERFLOW> Overflow -1209 <UPROCERR_DIVIDE> Divide by zero Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $power calculates the value of X raised to the power of Y ((XY). If X is less than zero, Y must be an integer. The absolute value of the result of $power must be in the range 10 -9999 through 10 9999 , inclusive. Example: Calculating a Cube Root The following example computes the cube root of the value in MYFIELD: vCubeRoot = $power(MYFIELD, 1/3) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}